sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Chat as AIChatInterface.tsx
    participant Backend as backend/api/idirs.py
    participant IDIRS as IDIRS OpenSearch<br/>localhost:8010
    participant Gemini as GeminiService

    Note over User,Gemini: /Dokumentsuche Flow (Hybrid Search)

    User->>Chat: /Dokumentsuche ref=AKTE-001 "query"
    Chat->>Chat: Parse filters + quoted query
    Chat->>Backend: POST /api/idirs/search<br/>{query, entity_filters, top_k}
    Backend->>IDIRS: POST /search<br/>(BM25 + kNN hybrid)
    IDIRS-->>Backend: Results with scores
    Backend-->>Chat: Formatted results
    Chat->>User: Markdown table<br/>(name, type, doc_id, score)

    Note over User,Gemini: /Dokumente-abfragen Flow (RAG + AI Analysis)

    User->>Chat: /Dokumente-abfragen docId1 "question"
    Chat->>Chat: Parse doc IDs + quoted question
    Chat->>Backend: POST /api/idirs/rag<br/>{doc_ids, question, language}
    loop For each doc_id
        Backend->>IDIRS: POST /rag<br/>{doc_id, question, top_k}
        IDIRS-->>Backend: Chunks + answer
    end
    Backend->>Backend: Calculate confidence<br/>(avg non-zero chunk scores)
    Backend->>Gemini: Analyze chunks + scores<br/>(language-specific prompt)
    Gemini-->>Backend: Structured analysis
    Backend->>Backend: Build disclaimer<br/>(>= 80%: green, < 80%: yellow)
    Backend-->>Chat: {analysis, confidence,<br/>disclaimer, chunk_count}
    Chat->>User: AI analysis + confidence badge<br/>+ disclaimer
